preparation for the Barbados conference, to create the 
Association of Caribbean States. A large group of foreign 
ministers and experts in foreign relations from the Caribbean 
and Latin America will finalize issues in Caracas for the 
forthcoming Association of Caribbean States convention and the 
Caricom summit for the Anglo-Caribbean community, which is to 
take place in Barbados in July. 

