Minh ESVEC [expansion unknown] in Jaruco Municipality. The 
materials were collected in a solidarity campaign sponsored by 
the UJC [Union of Young Communists] Ho Chi Minh Contingent and 
supported en masse by the Vietnamese people. 
  [LeDuc] "I can tell you the campaign is an example of the 
